      Contenido de la aplicacin
      1 error que corregir
      • Completa la seccin Contenido y audiencia objetivo
      Smart Decision (Decision Maker) When we need to make a decision, we can choose it random, consciously but without any criteria or without any methodology. Or maybe we choose do nothing and the opportunity is gone. What if you can take your mobile device, put the information you have and make the right decision for you with an statistical approach?. In other words, define your own criteria, evaluate your alternatives and make the best decision for you. As easy as that, in only 3 steps: 1 - Define criteria 2 - Evaluate your alternatives 3 - Make Smart Decision You will obtain: - An statistical result (not random). - See the ranking of your alternatives. - Three different approaches to choose: best alternative with restrictions, best alternative without restrictions and an additional one, the emotional decision. Smart Decision Center Beta- free. Version 0.96. Application for mobile platforms. This beta version is ready for you. You can try it if you want and all the comments before release 1.0 will be appreciate. All the functionalities will be working freely for you with limits only in the number of criterias you can define and the number of alternatives you may evaluate. For the commercial version (coming soon), you wont have this limits and you will can take advantage of more advanced capabilities under construction in this moment. For any comments please contact us at: kylconsultores@outlook.com
